song_name: I Dont Even Know Your Name
version_description: There wasn't a version for this song before so I've had a go at creating one. This is taken from the recording on Trampoline.
This interpretation of the colourful Cuban, Tex-Mex song, has added horn parts that can be played on the guitar. The Mavericks play it live, on Capo 3.

song_name: Heaven Or The Highway Out Of Town

version_description: Acoustic version. Song has a country feel and melody, suggest a country strum pattern. Listen to the video.

Easy to read acoustic version. Intro and instrumental parts are with chords. Song has a country feel listen to the video. A suggested strum pattern DUDU UDU, however others may work well. Acoustic version - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jhSRxEeyjfo.
